set.seed(3)
z <- round(rnorm(50) * 10)
summary(z)
##    Min. 1st Qu.  Median    Mean 3rd Qu.    Max. 
##  -23.00   -7.00   -1.50   -0.66    7.00   17.00
z[50] <- 40       # 50  40   
summary(z)
##    Min. 1st Qu.  Median    Mean 3rd Qu.    Max. 
##  -23.00   -7.00   -0.50    0.32    7.75   40.00
boxplot(z)
title(main="range = default(1.5)")

boxplot(z, range = 0) #      
title(main="range = 0")

boxplot(z, range = 1.0) # IQR   
title(main="range = 1.0")

boxplot(z, range = 2.0) # IQR * 2   
title(main="range = 2.0")

boxplot(z, outline = F, main = "outline = FALSE") #   

boxplot(z, outpch = 2) #
